# CLIENT

**Folder Structure**
root
├── public               # Public folder for static assets and HTML file
└── src
    ├── api              # API folder for creating axios instance and combining all request functions
    ├── assets           # Assets folder for keeping images, fonts, etc.
    ├── components       # Components folder for creating reusable components
    ├── config           # Configuration folder for application configuration files
    ├── redux            # Redux folder for managing Redux-related files (reducers, actions, store)
    ├── styles           # Styles folder for CSS, SCSS, or other styling files
    ├── tests            # Tests folder for unit tests, integration tests, etc.
    ├── utils            # Utils folder for utility/helper functions
    └── views            # Views folder for React components representing different views/screens
